          <option value="prisma" selected>Prisma-modus (matcht offici√´le Prisma-calculator)</option>
          <option value="rule">Vuistregel-modus (1 jet / 1% œÅ, baseline 131)</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label>Temperatuur (¬∞C)</label>
